1. *Pomoci* mi u učenju! (Help me with learning!)
2. Ona nam je pružila *pomoć* u rešavanju problema. (She provided us with help in solving the problem.)
3. Potrebna nam je *pomoć* da bismo to postigli. (We need help in order to achieve that.)
4. Oni su nam *pomogli* da izgradimo kuću. (They helped us to build a house.)
5. *Pomozi* nam da napravimo pravu odluku. (Help us to make the right decision.)